<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE GREAT PHYSICIAN</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hihdampa Lien tuhin anai,
 Lungsietna a dim Isu;
 Lungthim ngui kipak di'n A hilh,
 Aw ngai un, Isu aw chu!

[V2]
 Seraf-te zaila hawihpen,
 Mithiem sap theih min lulpen;
 Zaila laka hawihpen,
 Isu deihum Isu!

[V3]
 2. Na gitloh tam ngaihdam eitai,
 Aw ngai un Isu aw chuh!
 Lungmuong takin van gam zuon in,
 Lukhukkhu di'n Isu tawh.

[V4]
 3. Belam No thokit lopi hen,
 Tu'n Lal Isu ka gingta'i;
 Hukdampa min chu hawih ka sa'i,
 Isu min ka deihchuom hi.

[V5]
 4. A min in gitloh, lauh nawhmang,
 Lal Isu min thieng mai in;
 Aw ka tha a kipak na e,
 Isu min lun a het in.

[V6]
 5. Suohpih, pak la ei sakpih un,
 Aw Isu min chawian un;
 Hung un, suohpih, na awu suoh un,
 Aw Isu min chawian un.

[V7]
 6. Naupangte leh atek-akhang,
 Lal Isu min hehpihte;
 A sapna chuh tu'n pawm u hen,
 Isu di'n sem a, hing di'n.
 7. Chunglam khawvel vak a Isu,
 Mu di'n I chieh tieng uleh;
 Lungsiet chutphah kim a la sa'n,
 Lal Isu min chawian in.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>32</hymn_number>
</song>